Gene.FullName: SET domain and mariner transposase fusion gene

SubmitterDescription.SubmitterName: International Standards For Cytogenomic Arrays Consortium (ISCA)

SampleDescription.Description: mosaic - Metaphase FISH studies confirmed this deletion in 33.3% of metaphases and 27.0% of interphase nuclei from a PHA-stimulated culture as well as in 22.0% of interphase nuclei from a direct preparation. Phenotype: hypotonia, structural brain anomaly

ClinicalAssertion.StudyDescription: Copy number variation identified through the course of routine clinical cytogenomic testing in postnatal populations, with clinical assertions as classified by the original submitter.
